FBIS4-17314 "drsov079_g_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-079 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus State Oil Concern Chairman, Vice President Appointed State Oil Concern Chairman, Vice President Appointed WS2204092394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 1950 GMT 21 Apr 94 WS2204092394 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Belarusian BFN [Text] The Belarusian Council of Ministers has appointed Anton Loyka chairman of the Belarusian State Concern for Oil and Oil Products, relieving him from the duties of chairman of the Committee for Oil and Chemicals on whose basis the concern was formed. Alyaksandr Mahanik has been appointed first vice president.
